  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"18\">Category: Clan</strong><br data-start=\"18\" data-end=\"21\" /><strong data-start=\"21\" data-end=\"63\" data-is-only-node>Prerequisite: Ōtsutsuki Clan, Level 8+</strong></p><p data-start=\"67\" data-end=\"174\">You further enhance your innate abilities as an Ōtsutsuki, gaining new powers and refining existing ones.</p><ul data-start=\"176\" data-end=\"642\" data-is-last-node data-is-only-node><li data-start=\"176\" data-end=\"268\">Increase your Intelligence or Constitution score (your choice) by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li><li data-start=\"269\" data-end=\"642\" data-is-last-node><p>Select two from the following list:</p><ul data-start=\"311\" data-end=\"642\" data-is-last-node><li data-start=\"311\" data-end=\"384\">You gain an additional talent from the Ōtsutsuki Talent clan feature.</li><li data-start=\"387\" data-end=\"455\">You can change your Innate Chakra Shaping Jutsu on a Short Rest.</li><li data-start=\"458\" data-end=\"596\" data-is-only-node>Advanced Chakra Tools grants you a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with the weapon when cast, +2 at B-Rank, and +3 at S-Rank.</li><li data-start=\"599\" data-end=\"642\" data-is-last-node>Chakra Absorb increases its dice to 1d12.</li></ul></li></ul>",
